list_definition_mean.definitions_word_en: the powdered leaves of a tropical shrub, used as a dye to color the hair and decorate the body.
the Old World shrub which produces henna, with small pink, red, or white flowers.

list_definition_mean.definitions_ex_en: Renee hennaed my hair the night before the interview
list_definition_mean.definitions_ex_vn: Renee henna chúc được mái tóc của tôi đêm trước cuộc phỏng vấn
